      <title>特朗普关税冲击引发特鲁多战情室全体响应</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-26/donald-trump-tariff-shock-sparks-all-hands-response-in-justin-trudeau-war-room</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大财政部长克里斯蒂亚·弗里兰（Chrystia Freeland）周一晚上在渥太华结束有关美国关系的特别内阁会议时，出现了新的危机：唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）在社交媒体上发出关税威胁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-26/donald-trump-tariff-shock-sparks-all-hands-response-in-justin-trudeau-war-room</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 26 Nov 2024 17:46:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普关税威胁减弱贝森效应，美国国债下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-26/treasuries-slip-as-trump-s-tariff-threats-dim-the-bessent-effect</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在当选总统唐纳德·特朗普威胁对美国贸易伙伴征收额外关税之后，美国国债价格下跌，部分抹去了选择斯科特·贝森特出任财政部长所带来的收益。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-26/treasuries-slip-as-trump-s-tariff-threats-dim-the-bessent-effect</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 26 Nov 2024 16:47:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>标普 500 指数连续七天上涨，有望创下新高：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着投资者不再关注唐纳德·特朗普的关税计划，地缘政治风险逐渐减弱，股市创下历史新高。由于以色列与真主党停火的前景看好，油价下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Nov 2024 22:35:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
